  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and slice the <strong>carrots</strong> in half lengthways and then chop roughly</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>green lentils</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained lentils </strong>and <strong>sliced onion </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>ras el hanout </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give it a good mix<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>spiced lentils & carrot mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>spiced lentils & carrot mix </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the baking tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the lentils have started to crisp and the carrots are cooked through – these are your <strong>crispy spiced lentils & carrots</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half</p><p>Peel 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>orange</strong> and slice into segments</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>in<strong> </strong>a large bowl with<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>rocket </strong>and <strong>orange segments </strong>to the<strong> </strong>dressing with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Crumble in the <strong>Greek cheese </strong>– this is your <strong>orange & Greek cheese salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and<strong> harissa</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl – this is your <strong>harissa yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-spiced-lentil-and-carrot-bake/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy spiced lentils & carrots </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>harissa yoghurt</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>orange & Greek cheese salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
